graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Pod (per InferenceService)"
        direction LR
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh<br/>Orchestration Layer]
        Adapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC]
        Server[Model Server<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO/TorchServe]
        RESTProxy[REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]

        ModelMesh -->|loads/unloads| Adapter
        Adapter -->|8001/TCP gRPC| Server
        RESTProxy -->|translates to| ModelMesh
        OAuthProxy -->|forwards to| RESTProxy
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        ISVC[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        Predictor[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntime[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntime[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| ISVC
    User -->|creates| Predictor
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntime

    ISVC -->|watched by| Controller
    Predictor -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntime -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntime -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| RuntimeDeployment[Runtime Deployment]
    RuntimeDeployment -->|contains| ModelMesh

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|depends on| etcd[etcd<br/>Key-Value Store]
    ModelMesh -->|metadata| etcd
    Server -->|downloads models| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Controller -->|integrates| Dashboard[RHOAI Dashboard]
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates| OSAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    Controller -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2
    style ModelMesh fill:#4a90e2
    style ISVC fill:#f5a623
    style Predictor fill:#f5a623
    style ServingRuntime fill:#f5a623
    style ClusterServingRuntime fill:#f5a623
    style etcd fill:#e8e8e8
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321
    style OSAuth fill:#7ed321
